==Serbian==
===Etymology===
A [[Slavic]] ([[Serbian]] and [[Croatian]]) male name meaning ''mountain man'' or ''man from the mountain'' that comes from the word ''[[gora]]'', meaning ''mountain''
===Proper noun===
'''Горан'''
#A male [[given name]].
